                  <summary>An undated copy of a geographical work entitle <title>Haft Iqlīm</title> (Seven Climes) authored by <persName key="person_232008283" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/232008283/" xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc">Amīn Aḥmad al-Rāzī, fl. 1593-1619</persName>, 
